@ApiAggregator_HostAddress = http://localhost:5166

### Get JWT Token
POST {{ApiAggregator_HostAddress}}/api/auth/token
Accept: application/json

### Get Aggregated Data (requires token)
# Copy the token from the previous response and set it as the Bearer token below
GET {{ApiAggregator_HostAddress}}/api/aggregated?pageSize=5
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Aggregated Data - Filter by category
GET {{ApiAggregator_HostAddress}}/api/aggregated?category=Weather&pageSize=5
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Aggregated Data - Filter by search term
GET {{ApiAggregator_HostAddress}}/api/aggregated?search=quantum&sortBy=date&sortOrder=desc
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Request Statistics
GET {{ApiAggregator_HostAddress}}/api/statistics
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
